::Perndabot::

Perndabot turns back to look at the Cybertronian Fire, which was now 
pretty far away.

"Well, we're out," he says to BrightBlade, looking her over again as 
he uncloaks. He sighs, the huge bot a bit dissapointed.

"Do you have to go back to the Predacons?"
